{"tid":491019,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"斥中超嚴重腐敗 買通裁判　球員打假波","createTime":"2017-12-06T06:19:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-06T10:33:23.000Z","uid":25558,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2771070106cc9f8c8c5c4452cf65f69c948c5fd6","tid":491019,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T06:19:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20171206/20236063\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171206%2F20236063&d=06gfd3pA%2Fau4FvtBh%2FCmGlzEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=c59edb13\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171206%2F20236063&h=8f69c280\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20171206/20236063</a><br />\n<br />\n斥中超嚴重腐敗<br />\n買通裁判　球員打假波<br />\n<br />\n兩岸要聞   <br />\n       <img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171206/large/06cx04p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171206%2Flarge%2F06cx04p.jpg&h=e2c6ff8a&s={SIZE}\" />  <br />\n<br />\n國足被指體制問題令實力大打折扣。<br />\n「自2011年全運會足球比賽就開始和足協官員勾結吹假波。」中國泱泱大國，足球事業乏善足陳。內地評論直斥制度害人，行政管理主導市場的雙軌制是罪魁禍首，令中國足球聯賽出現官商勾結、假波黑哨等醜聞。<br />\n<br />\n促改革體制<br />\n<br />\n《方圓》雜誌大肆鞭撻中超足球聯賽貪腐現象：「要論操縱比賽的腐敗程度，無疑是中超足球聯賽最為嚴重──賄賂高官、買通裁判，甚至買通對手打假波、打黑波，是一些足球俱樂部的慣用手段。」報道亦引述著名裁判陸俊刑拘後供詞稱：「自2011年全運會足球比賽就開始和足協官員勾結吹假波。」報道指出，內地足球推行職業化已經20年，市場運作商業化，管理則是行政體制，由行政管理主導市場化運作的雙軌制，令中國足球聯賽出現官商勾結、假波黑哨等醜聞。<br />\n<br />\n此外，中國足球一系列腐敗醜聞中，足協官員在贊助商洽談中存在利益輸送的情況，經營體育賽事成為部份貪官中飽私囊的利器。專家建議改革體制，體育部門簡政放權，認為權力一旦下放給市場，體育官員不再有尋租的空間。<br />\n<br />\n《方圓》雜誌<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n<br />\n\t最高檢揭國家體育局黑幕得罪領導　田亮得分有上限<br />\n兩岸要聞 8小時前"},{"pid":"dc22a143e5e88e57381cf28d0fab36f209292f9e","tid":491019,"uid":43173,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T06:29:53.000Z","msg":"這算是新聞嗎？"},{"pid":"4cc53178c447412d9cdb5577609c836201ee709c","tid":491019,"uid":3646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T06:37:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>這算是新聞嗎？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f50c36b94bdefc104e2df9a828d868fb0f328eb","tid":491019,"uid":93784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T06:39:32.000Z","msg":"中國做呢D野不嬲係最出色 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81b765e14ad55470eac0ba841458be1edee3a98f","tid":491019,"uid":6751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T06:39:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>這算是新聞嗎？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fc083605a39c397d4f709ad33fd42584a7881a7","tid":491019,"uid":108421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T06:45:25.000Z","msg":"我等緊一張圖"},{"pid":"ba913452ab0d01c73da0c973a762ec56b8d42f97","tid":491019,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T07:27:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>這算是新聞嗎？</blockquote><br />\n支那唔貪先係新聞"},{"pid":"e22856fc2eba25ff0704e49da3001fb59eb216e2","tid":491019,"uid":45788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":